{"tid":1820223,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人要識中田敦彥","createTime":"2020-01-11T11:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T14:33:33.000Z","uid":186882,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"322305e8783d10721d6942690e94b1133a36d24e","tid":1820223,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T11:53:03.000Z","msg":"講香港示威好多人都講過<br />\n但可以極有條理咁將中國近代史<br />\n極之有條理咁鋪排<br />\n短短兩節一小時講哂整個中國，台灣，新疆，西藏，以至香港<br />\n不論人物，事件，鋪排都極有條理<br />\n<br />\n真真正正中國近代史超級懶人包<br />\n<br />\n唔單止日本人要識佢，整個東亞既人都要識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Qok491jX8LI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQok491jX8LI&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=ddb23413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Qok491jX8LI</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EDfK6uN20ts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEDfK6uN20ts&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=98572c5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EDfK6uN20ts</a>"},{"pid":"fb4f42e96e9ea1e6f130f7c991518d388a9a0d07","tid":1820223,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T11:57:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=f0b09ca4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美國議員講野無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><