br />\n睇完更加令我明白點解日本人咁鍾意中國歷史<br />\n因為喺日本人眼中，中國歷史應該係人類史上最痴撚線既歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/o0mdQ9wl7qw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fo0mdQ9wl7qw&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=30c504c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/o0mdQ9wl7qw</a><br />\n<br />\n呢堂我聽完之後真係丁一聲<br />\n半個鐘已經起哂秦朝既超級懶人包<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街中國五千年暴政歷史同權鬥<br />\n早喺秦始皇時期已經無改變過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌那星真係乜撚野低劣基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T18:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又有嘢學，好撚正"},{"pid":"33cd69e517a122bdd8805314b567d2918e1d9b8d","tid":1820223,"uid":254838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T18:10:47.000Z","msg":"學到嘢，多謝"},{"pid":"997c120326007b406d1845611cb847cf1d0b1189","tid":1820223,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T18:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6d9645304f326fa499aa277cd2b8ad4c8bbd1d","tid":1820223,"uid":186882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T20:08:07.000Z","msg":"唔係淨係中國歷史先至要識中田敦彥<br />\n世界歷史，國際關係，政治，經濟，甚至文學，哲學都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱又聽埋呢個講日本消費稅<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BHt32bB1Dqw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBHt32bB1Dqw&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=06c885d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BHt32bB1Dqw</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JWluc9xSmqU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJWluc9xSmqU&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=578460fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JWluc9xSmqU</a><br />\n<br />\n超級簡易版了解日本經濟既政治操作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽完我覺得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家可以聯想下，五毛日日講到日本經濟沉咗20年<br />\n國債清極都唔完<br />\n<br />\n事實上日本係味真係咁淒涼呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，超級感謝NYT Global既字幕組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL7nT0kaCNG5J8G3yAniIZV6t_UkalOziR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPL7nT0kaCNG5J8G3yAniIZV6t_UkalOziR&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=46e811aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL7nT0kaCNG5J8G3yAniIZV6t_UkalOziR</a><br />\n<br />\n期待佢地可以翻譯埋中田先生講兩韓，中美貿易戰，中東局勢既課堂"},{"pid":"b602f9c22a4584bc2f4d3c0d0ca57c20342d2c19","tid":1820223,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9de6688c1096581b9015caabb0e5ff423aece069","tid":1820223,"uid":38570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69ee26605d69cbf34f4b04dac6fa6b664575e79e","tid":1820223,"uid":150610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T16:57:26.000Z","msg":"好高汁，似佢咁講，習同毛有啲似，又係冇料同不切實際既夢想家 + 無人性既獨裁者"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T17:42:32.000Z","msg":"毛魔絕對唔會係無料"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:18:45.000Z","msg":"佢既料去晒鬥爭度,唔係治國之才"},{"pid":"8c35999e725abbd5ff329962d4fe1ea10f73d21d","tid":1820223,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b602f9c22a4584bc2f4d3c0d0ca57c20342d2c19","tid":1820223,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9de6688c1096581b9015caabb0e5ff423aece069","tid":1820223,"uid":38570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69ee26605d69cbf34f4b04dac6fa6b664575e79e","tid":1820223,"uid":150610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T16: